					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The SNES Mouse protocol is documented in both the <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Mouse" class="postlink">NesDevWiki</a> and in the <a href="http://wiki.superfamicom.org/snes/show/Controllers#mouse" class="postlink">Super Famicom Wiki</a>. NoCash also has a <a href="http://nocash.emubase.de/fullsnes.htm#snescontrollersmousetwobuttonmouse" class="postlink">writeup</a>.</div>

